Did you call for any further assistance? - My mistress came up as far as the door; she was frightened and went d own again;
Mary Pope
the lodger up two pair of stairs came to her.

Mr. CHARTER. The woman never made any such declaration to me, nor never said any thing like it, nor never made any such enquiry;
Patrick Foy
came and told me that she had said so.

In what pieces? - Nine guineas and a half, and the rest in silver; my watch was in my breeches pocket under the bed;
Thomas Oliver
slept in the same room in another bed; the maid locked the door on the outside.
